Issue: Copypaste from Host OS to VM in virtualbox not working
Solution (steps):
1. Enable bidirectional data in General->Advanced setting of VM
2. Install VBoxClient (requirement for next step): sudo apt install virtualbox-guest-x11
3. Restart the VBox clipboard module: pkill 'VBoxClient --clipboard' -f & sleep 1 && VBoxClient --clipboard

Issue: mininet-vm (mininet-2.3.0-210211-ubuntu-18.04.5-server-amd64) GUI install
Solution:
1. sudo apt-get update
2. sudo apt-get install xinit x11-xserver-utils mate-desktop-environment-core (minmal mate-desktop)
3. sudo apt-get install virtualbox-guest-x11 (if running on virtualbox)

